Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png'}
{3: 'I heard a voice in the dark, so I opened my eyes.'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory189.png'}
{2: 'Where is this place?', 3: '9', 4: '(Look around)', 5: '10'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "We are underneath the Demon General's Castle. I'm so glad that you are awake, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'This place looked like an underground facility. Lucia and others looked happy and relieved.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Hehe, I was so scared just now. Didn't expect this game to have the bleeding feature. You wouldn't have survived without Karenina's recovery potions.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina?', 3: '12', 4: 'The potions they collected all along...', 5: '13'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Yeah, two of you dropped from above. Don't you remember?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'So you really were collecting the potions... The villagers thought we were bad guys because of that.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Whatever, now that the Commandant of Gray Raven is awake, can we leave this place already?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Karenina walked out of darkness and looked at Lucia. She seemed to be quite upset.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Before taking action, we need to at least explain the situation to Commandant, like why we were here, and what happened.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'What a hassle.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Commandant, you just woke up, so you may feel a little weak. You only need to listen.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'First of all, just like you expected, we had a fight with the King.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "But somehow our attacks didn't work at all. At the most crucial moment, we saw two of you falling down from the castle.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: '...As well as some bombs left by Camu and Vera.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Those two would do anything just to win...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "And you said you wanted to finish us off at the spawn point! You aren't any different!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "I don't do cheap shots!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Those bombs seemed to be taken off Demons. Anyway, they landed before the King's attack, so the land blocks all collapsed, and we ended up here.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'The bleeding was also from falling. But now you should be fine.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Did anyone come after us?', 3: '27', 4: 'What were Vera and Camu thinking...', 5: '28'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Not yet, but the King probably knows we are here. We can't stay long.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "Who knows what those two maniacs were thinking? I'm so going to beat them up next time I see them.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Anyway, a lot of things are still unknown. Commandant, we may belong to different teams, but I think we should move together.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'System', 3: '【kuroname】 has joined the team.'}
